<section class="container">
  <h2>Selected Case Studies</h2>

  <div class="case-study">
    <h3>Qolo, Inc — Building People Ops from Zero</h3>
    <p><strong>Context:</strong> Series A fintech startup scaling fast with no formal HR or recruiting infrastructure.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Grew headcount from 20 → 114 in under 12 months</li>
      <li>Built TA and HR functions from scratch</li>
      <li>Implemented Greenhouse, compensation bands, and people programs</li>
      <li>Earned Great Place to Work certification</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Scalable, compliant, people-first organization aligned with business growth.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="case-study">
    <h3>MediaMath — Global Engineering Hiring Reset</h3>
    <p><strong>Context:</strong> Engineering pipeline stalled across international teams.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Hired 12 engineers globally in first 90 days</li>
      <li>Redesigned interview process to a 3-step panel</li>
      <li>Reduced candidate drop-off and leadership time investment</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Faster hiring, higher acceptance rates, restored confidence in TA.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="case-study">
    <h3>Wagmo — First Recruiter, Immediate Impact</h3>
    <p><strong>Context:</strong> Early-stage company preparing for Series B.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Closed 3 revenue-driving sales roles in first 30 days</li>
      <li>Built hiring frameworks across Sales, Engineering, and Analytics</li>
      <li>Partnered directly with COO and executive leadership</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Hiring foundation built for next phase of growth.</p>
  </div>
</section>

